'''Zoophilic''' means liking or preferring [[animal]]s.

Zoophilic [[organism]]s are found primarily in animals and cause marked [[inflammation|inflammatory]] reactions in humans who have contact with infected [[cat]]s, [[dog]]s, [[cattle]], [[horse]]s, [[bird]]s, or other animals. This is followed by a rapid termination of the [[infection]].


